[{"information_id":"4","bottom":"1","sort_order":"1","status":"1","language_id":"1","title":"About Us","description":"&lt;div class=&quot;about-veil-container&quot;&gt;\r\n    &lt;h1 style=&quot;border-bottom: 2px solid #a89081; padding-bottom: 10px; margin-bottom: 30px;&quot;&gt;VEIL&lt;\/h1&gt;\r\n    &lt;p style=&quot;font-size: 18px; color: #a89081; font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 20px;&quot;&gt;VEIL ISN'T JUST A LABEL, IT'S A BLACKOUT OF THE NOISE.&lt;\/p&gt;\r\n    &lt;p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8;&quot;&gt;Born from the shadows of the street and refined for the modern vanguard, we bridge the gap between high-fashion silhouettes and raw urban utility. Our mission is simple: &lt;strong&gt;DISTILL THE AESTHETIC.&lt;\/strong&gt;&lt;\/p&gt;\r\n    &lt;div style=&quot;background: #1a1a1a; padding: 25px; border-left: 4px solid #a89081;&quot;&gt;\r\n        &lt;h3 style=&quot;margin-top: 0;&quot;&gt;MONOCHROMATIC POWER&lt;\/h3&gt;\r\n        &lt;p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0;&quot;&gt;We don't do loud logos or fleeting trends. Every drop at VEIL is a curated statement\u2014built for those who move through the city with intent and style.&lt;\/p&gt;\r\n    &lt;\/div&gt;\r\n&lt;\/div&gt;","meta_title":"About Us","meta_description":"","meta_keyword":""},{"information_id":"6","bottom":"1","sort_order":"2","status":"1","language_id":"1","title":"Delivery Information","description":"&lt;div class=&quot;about-veil-container&quot;&gt;\r\n    &lt;h1 style=&quot;border-bottom: 2px solid #a89081; padding-bottom: 10px; margin-bottom: 30px;&quot;&gt;LOGISTICS OF THE DROP&lt;\/h1&gt;\r\n    \r\n    &lt;p style=&quot;font-size: 18px; color: #a89081; font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 20px;&quot;&gt;\r\n        VEIL OPERATES ON A PRECISION-FIRST DELIVERY MODEL.\r\n    &lt;\/p&gt;\r\n    \r\n    &lt;p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 30px; line-height: 1.8;&quot;&gt;\r\n        Every piece of monochromatic utility is dispatched with the same intent it was designed with. We ensure your gear moves through the urban grid efficiently, arriving in our signature discreet, weather-resistant packaging.\r\n    &lt;\/p&gt;\r\n\r\n    &lt;div style=&quot;background: #1a1a1a; padding: 25px; border-left: 4px solid #a89081; margin-bottom: 30px;&quot;&gt;\r\n        &lt;h3 style=&quot;margin-top: 0;&quot;&gt;SHIPPING STANDARDS&lt;\/h3&gt;\r\n        &lt;ul style=&quot;list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; color: #eee;&quot;&gt;\r\n            &lt;li style=&quot;margin-bottom: 10px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;PROCESSING:&lt;\/strong&gt; 24-48 HOURS FROM DROP TIME.&lt;\/li&gt;\r\n            &lt;li style=&quot;margin-bottom: 10px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;FLAT RATE:&lt;\/strong&gt; 5.00\u20ac NATIONWIDE.&lt;\/li&gt;\r\n            &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ELITE STATUS:&lt;\/strong&gt; FREE SHIPPING ON ORDERS OVER 60.00\u20ac.&lt;\/li&gt;&lt;\/ul&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;\r\n&lt;\/div&gt;","meta_title":"Delivery Information","meta_description":"","meta_keyword":""},{"information_id":"3","bottom":"1","sort_order":"3","status":"1","language_id":"1","title":"Privacy Policy","description":"&lt;div class=&quot;about-veil-container&quot;&gt;\r\n    &lt;h1 style=&quot;border-bottom: 2px solid #a89081; padding-bottom: 10px; margin-bottom: 30px;&quot;&gt;IDENTITY ENCRYPTION&lt;\/h1&gt;\r\n    \r\n    &lt;p style=&quot;font-size: 18px; color: #a89081; font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 20px;&quot;&gt;\r\n        AT VEIL, YOUR ANONYMITY IS OUR STANDARD.\r\n    &lt;\/p&gt;\r\n    \r\n    &lt;p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 30px; line-height: 1.8;&quot;&gt;\r\n        Moving through the digital grid requires a high level of security. We respect your privacy as much as your aesthetic, ensuring that all data remains encrypted and under the VEIL. We only collect what is necessary to get the drop to your door.\r\n    &lt;\/p&gt;\r\n\r\n    &lt;div style=&quot;background: #1a1a1a; padding: 25px; border-left: 4px solid #a89081; margin-bottom: 30px;&quot;&gt;\r\n        &lt;h3 style=&quot;margin-top: 0;&quot;&gt;DATA PROTOCOLS&amp;nbsp;&lt;\/h3&gt;\r\n        &lt;ul style=&quot;list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; color: #eee;&quot;&gt;\r\n            &lt;li style=&quot;margin-bottom: 10px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ENCRYPTION:&lt;\/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;All checkout data is handled via secure protocols.&lt;\/li&gt;\r\n            &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SECURE PAYMENTS:&lt;\/strong&gt; Your financial details are processed through encrypted channels.&lt;\/li&gt;&lt;\/ul&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;\r\n&lt;\/div&gt;","meta_title":"Privacy Policy","meta_description":"","meta_keyword":""},{"information_id":"5","bottom":"1","sort_order":"4","status":"1","language_id":"1","title":"Terms &amp; Conditions","description":"&lt;div class=&quot;about-veil-container&quot;&gt;\r\n    &lt;h1 style=&quot;border-bottom: 2px solid #a89081; padding-bottom: 10px; margin-bottom: 30px;&quot;&gt;THE PROTOCOL&lt;\/h1&gt;\r\n    \r\n    &lt;p style=&quot;font-size: 18px; color: #a89081; font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 20px;&quot;&gt;\r\n        BY ACCESSING THE GRID, YOU AGREE TO THE STANDARDS.\r\n    &lt;\/p&gt;\r\n    \r\n    &lt;p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 30px; line-height: 1.8;&quot;&gt;\r\n        All operations within the VEIL store are governed by these protocols. We reserve the right to modify the grid and its contents at any time without prior notice. Usage of our digital platform constitutes your full acceptance of these terms.\r\n    &lt;\/p&gt;\r\n\r\n    &lt;div style=&quot;background: #1a1a1a; padding: 25px; border-left: 4px solid #a89081; margin-bottom: 30px;&quot;&gt;\r\n        &lt;h3 style=&quot;margin-top: 0;&quot;&gt;OPERATIONAL TERMS&lt;\/h3&gt;\r\n        &lt;ul style=&quot;list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; color: #eee;&quot;&gt;\r\n            &lt;li style=&quot;margin-bottom: 10px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;INTELLECTUAL PROPERTY:&lt;\/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;All designs, imagery, and code are the exclusive property of VEIL.&lt;\/li&gt;\r\n            &lt;li style=&quot;margin-bottom: 10px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ORDER FINALITY:&lt;\/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;Once a drop is confirmed, modifications may restricted due to logistics.&lt;\/li&gt;\r\n            &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;LIMITATION OF LIABILITY:&lt;\/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;We are not responsible for errors arising from external server issues.&lt;\/li&gt;&lt;\/ul&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;\r\n&lt;\/div&gt;","meta_title":"Terms &amp; Conditions","meta_description":"","meta_keyword":""}]